{"fadeType":2,"once":true,"scripts":[{"mode":1,"stopbgm":true,"sequence":[["Superstar of the Blue Seas\n\n<size=45>Chapter 3 - Protectors of the Seal<\/size>",1]]},{"flashout":{"dur":1,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Hmm, I'm almost sure it headed in this direction...","dir":1,"bgm":"story-1","side":2,"bgmDelay":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"delay":1,"dur":1,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","actor":107034},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Following the reported sightings of the Seal, I thought we had managed to get a good lead on the Seal's whereabouts.","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"expression":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"We're getting close, Commander! I know it!","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","actor":107034},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Sorry, Commander, but I'll have to ask you to stop there for a moment.","actor":105140,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Right, uh... \"We are the Protectors of the Seal.\"","actor":105190,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"\"If you want to pass through here, then you must first answer our question.\"","actor":105200,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"\"We will not give the Seal's location to evildoers who cannot answer this question.\"","actor":105140,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"They spoke in a lazy manner, like a bored voice actor just phoning in their lines...","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"So, the question is: what family does the earless seal belong to?","dir":1,"side":2,"options":[{"flag":1,"content":"\"Phocidae.\""},{"flag":2,"content":"\"Panthera maritimus?\""},{"flag":3,"content":"\"I'd like to use a lifeline for this one... Saratoga?\""}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","actor":105200},{"expression":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Wow! Spot on, Commander!","dir":1,"side":2,"action":[{"type":"shake","y":30,"delay":0,"dur":0.15,"number":2,"x":0}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"actor":107034,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","optionFlag":1},{"expression":5,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"That's like bad Latin for \"sea lion\"! Also, sea lions have ear flaps! The correct answer is \"Phocidae\"!","dir":1,"side":2,"action":[{"type":"shake","y":30,"delay":0,"dur":0.15,"number":2,"x":0}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"actor":107034,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","optionFlag":2},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Heh heh! The answer is \"Phocidae\"!","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":107034,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","optionFlag":3},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Ding ding ding. All right, you can move along.","actor":105200,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"It seems like they'll let us pass now.","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"expression":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"... Pfft! I never imagined you three would do something like this!","dir":1,"side":2,"action":[{"type":"shake","y":30,"delay":0,"dur":0.15,"number":2,"x":0}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","actor":107034},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"... So? It's fun.","actor":105190,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"They said it would be fun, and I'm along for the ride, so to speak.","actor":105140,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"expression":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"You not enjoyin' yourself, sis?","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","actor":105200},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"That's not what I meant. I am enjoying this, as it's for a charitable cause.","actor":105140,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Well, there's nothing wrong with having some fun at the same time! I bet many will struggle with that question!","actor":107034,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"expression":3,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Oh, by the way, how are the preparations coming along?","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","actor":107034},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"They're going well. Don't worry.","actor":105140,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Great to hear~! Thanks for covering for me~","actor":107034,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"(What \"preparations\" are they talking about...?)","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"expression":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Okay, Commander! Let's move on!","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"actor":107034,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","blackBg":true}],"mode":2,"fadein":1.5,"id":"SALATUOJIAHAIBAO3","fadeOut":1.5}